horse_wood_wall_decor_hooks_6_pieces_set.name: Horse Wood Wall Decor Hooks 6 Pieces Set

Dimensions: 8.38" H x 21.25" W x 3.25" D
Material: Resin & Metal
Shape: Novelty
Color: Gray, Brown, Beige & Black
Orientation: Horizontal
